updated epos using existing myerp DB

0. mkdir epos2
1. git clone https://github.com/Tranco1/epos2.git
2. cd epos2
3. sudo apt install nodejs ( if not installed )

for the frontend:

4. npm create vite@latest epos2 -- --template react
5. cd epos2
6. npm install
7. npm install axios

for the backend

8. mkdir server && cd server
9. npm init -y
10. npm install express pg cors body-parser
   cd epos2
11. npm install bcrypt   ( encryption )
12. npm install bcrypt jsonwebtoken
13. npm install react-router-dom  (provide routing for login page )
14. npm install lucide-react  ( This is the hamburger menu )

15. Check the dependancies in the project root package.json file.
